p.01703376c4a81c0e9d91: Returns the tag of an object.
p.01703376c4a81c0e9d92:
Provides the tag that uniquely identifies the object.

Each instance of data or brick is identified by a unique identifier.
"Code as data" implies that each brick instance in a project is an instance of a Marketplace brick and is identified with a unique tag.
The same principle goes for a data instance in a dataset.
Tags can be accessed in the Draw user interface via a project's brick dropdown menu item "Show Tag" or in the Data Set "Tag" column.
The object whose tag to retrieve.
